747
00:46:15,140 --> 00:46:17,475
Another lowercase "I,"

748
00:46:19,444 --> 00:46:23,815
with a line ruled under it
and four uppercase S's.

749
00:46:23,915 --> 00:46:27,618
Scratch that.
