00:47:01,286 --> 00:47:05,223
so I could see what was
originally on the page.

764
00:47:06,257 --> 00:47:07,993
It doesn't give us
a lot to work with, huh?

765
00:47:08,093 --> 00:47:09,995
KINCAID: It's like
a crossword puzzle

