772
00:47:21,873 --> 00:47:22,874
By the way,

773
00:47:22,974 --> 00:47:24,910
next time I tell you to move,

774
00:47:25,010 --> 00:47:28,914
move, or I'll leave you behind.

775
00:47:29,014 --> 00:47:32,317
I need to run this
through my lab at home.

