00:48:44,922 --> 00:48:46,958
And Margaret's gonna
stay here with you.

796
00:48:47,392 --> 00:48:49,160
Okay?

797
00:48:49,260 --> 00:48:52,163
All right, everyone get
acquainted. I'll be right back.

