00:53:54,565 --> 00:53:56,209
And it's in the best
interests of the children

903
00:53:56,233 --> 00:53:57,578
for Joan to have
primary custody right now.

904
00:53:57,602 --> 00:54:00,271
We have a child who
is still traumatized

